        Docker Ecosytem
 ________________________________
|               |               |
| Docker Client | Docker Server |
|_______________|_______________|   
|               |               |
| Docker Machine| Docker Images |
|_______________|_______________|
|               |               |
| Docker Hub    | Docker Compose|
|_______________|_______________|

Docker is a platform or ecosystem
around creating and running containers.

                                                   ___________  
                                                  |           |
                                  ________________| Container |
 __________                      |                |___________|
|          |                     |       
|  Docker  |_____________________|                Instance of an image.
|  Image   |                     |                Runs a program.
|__________|                     |                 ___________ 
                                 |________________|           |
                                                  | Container |
                                                  |___________|
Single file with all
the dependencies and
config required to run
a program.